title: Who is Jennifer O’Brien? TikTok influencer jailed for 17 years after court confirms at least 10 serious crimes
summary_full: TikTok creator Jennifer O’Brien, known online as Jennifer Nieve, has been jailed for 17 years after a Manchester court found she physically abused a woman at least 10 times. The judge called the crimes repeated and deeply harmful. The victim described long-term fear and anxiety. The case was reported by the Manchester Evening News.
